                        .tag.ui UI
                        .tag.uxr UXR
                        .tag.fd Dev
                        .tag.ai AI

                    h4(data-title="Impact") Impact
                    p Replaced $200–300/year SaaS proofing platforms with a self-hosted tool built around how photography clients actually make selection decisions. Clients stopped sending "can you compare #47 and #52?" emails — they were doing that comparison themselves and arriving with a confident, exportable selection. Multiple photographers in the community have expressed interest in purchasing the tool once it reaches a stable, distributable state, validating that the gap it fills is wider than one studio. Shipped in 2 days using Claude AI for rapid full-stack prototyping — no Figma-to-developer handoff required.

